Hungary’s BUX Stock Index Rebounds, Reversing Earlier Losses

-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 
2011-07-12T13:00:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/hungary-s-bux-stock-index-rebounds-reversing-earlier-losses.html
Hungarian stocks rose, snapping two
days of losses and reversing earlier declines.  The benchmark BUX index of shares rose 0.2 percent to
21,866.04 by 2:52 p.m. in Budapest, after losing as much as 1.9
percent. Mol Nyrt., the country’s biggest refiner, rose 2.6
percent to 20,700 forint.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andras Gergely in Budapest 
 agergely@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at   gserkin@bloomberg.net  